title: Untouchable-Power Corrupts - Season 1
description:
Untouchable-Power Corrupts - Season 1

This dramatic reconstruction series unravels the shockingly true stories of people in authority who committed some of the worst crimes imaginable. These supposed 'pillars of society' became criminals and then abused their positions of power.

Each standalone episode retells one twisting, turning case of a leading figure's crime and their attempt to evade capture, before justice was served.

Just how did each perpetrator commit these unbelievable crimes and imagine they could get away with it? Each scandalous story is recounted first-hand by the investigators, and people who helped put them behind bars.

Ep 1 - White Coat, Dark Heart
Ep 2 - House Of Pain
Ep 3 - Teflon Joe
Ep 4 - Courtroom Killer
Ep 5 - Mobster Cop
Ep 6 - Ballot & Bullet
